name: Red union 6
description: It seems so easy to be honest. But is it really that simple? Is it so easy to show a candid photo when you stopped loving every part of your body? Is it so easy to talk frankly to people when you’ve already been deceived 1,000 times? Is it so easy to walk down the street in plain clothes when you’re followed by indecent words. No. That’s why my manifesto number six is about honesty. I don’t care about anyone who doesn’t like anything – the most important is being honest with yourself.
